sentences: Tamko later attended City College of New York and graduated from the Grove School of Engineering in 2015.
In 2014 she started uploading her music to Bandcamp under the pseudonym Vagabon.
In addition to vocals and guitar, Tamko played drums, keyboard, and synth on her 2017 album Infinite Worlds.
In 2018 she was invited to open for Courtney Barnett on her North American summer tour.
